36  public class Johab_OLD  extends Charset
37  {
38  
39      public Johab_OLD() {
40          super("x-Johab-OLD", null);
41      }
42  
43      public boolean contains(Charset cs) {
44          return ((cs.name().equals("US-ASCII"))
45                  || (cs instanceof Johab_OLD));
46      }
47  
48      public CharsetDecoder newDecoder() {
49          return new Decoder(this);
50      }
51  
52      public CharsetEncoder newEncoder() {
53          return new Encoder(this);
54      }
55  
56  
57      /**
58       * These accessors are temporarily supplied while sun.io
59       * converters co-exist with the sun.nio.cs.{ext} charset coders
60       * These facilitate sharing of conversion tables between the
61       * two co-existing implementations. When sun.io converters
62       * are made extinct these will be unncessary and should be removed
63       */
64  
65      public short[] getDecoderIndex1() {
66          return Decoder.index1;
67      }
68  
69      public String[] getDecoderIndex2() {
70          return Decoder.index2;
71  
72      }
73  
74      public short[] getEncoderIndex1() {
75          return Encoder.index1;
76  
77      }
78      public String[] getEncoderIndex2() {
79          return Encoder.index2;
80  
81      }
